cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on improving depth completion using neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of self-attention mechanism and boundary consistency also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the application of depth completion has relevance to robotics (cs.RO) for tasks such as navigation and object recognition.
